snippet.title: Sega Ages 2500 Series Vol. 25: Gunstar Heroes Treasure Box (PS2 Gameplay)
snippet.description:
This game is a compilation of Treasure's games developed for SEGA during the 16-bit generation emulated for the PS2's hardware and released under the SEGA AGES label. The games included are  Gunstar Heroes, Dynamite Headdy, and Alien Soldier.
All games come with different display options (such as texture filtering and such) to suit the gamer's need, as well as digital sound and your choice between playing the Japanese original versions or their overseas counterparts.
